CatDescriptText: Cutline of related image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, December 29, 1962, pg. 20, reads: "Limbo, Everybody! - ...at the annual Christmas party of the American Woodmen. Limbo and twisting highlighted the afternoon of Christmas activities."
TitMainTitle: Girls, and boys, including boy wearing light colored knitted hat, standing in lines behind rectangular table, with men and women on other side, at Christmas party sponsored by American Woodmen
